title: Pacifica Radio Voices that Changed the World spoken word collect
description:
Collection from Pacifica Radio's archives of shows from 1997-2003. Includes detailed index in xls and csv file. About 1,350 hours of audio recordings in MP3 format on a wide variety of topics: arts, literature, politics, feminism, philosophy, audio books, religion...

Some of the many notable contributors include:
Angela Davis
Cornel West
Noam Chomsky
Malcolm X
Ralph Nader
Studs Terkel
Howard Zinn
Alan Watts
Gore Vidal
Edward Said
